OL,5, The energy secretary says he is "very  
OL,6, sympathetic" to suggestions that the   
OL,7, government should stop a planned #500  
OL,8, rise in annual energy bills from April.
OL,10,FGrant Shapps said he was working "hard"
OL,11,Fwith Chancellor Jeremy Hunt on the     
OL,12,Fissue.                                 
OL,14,FThere are warnings that a million more 
OL,15,Fhouseholds could struggle if bills go  
OL,16,Fup again.                              
OL,18,FThe government is limiting the typical 
OL,19,Fannual energy bill to #2,500, but this 
OL,20,Fwill increase to #3,000 from 1 April.  
